PLUGIN
=======
Kalkun use combination of Hook-based and HMVC (Hierarchical Model View Controller) Plugin System.
All plugins is stored at /application/plugins.

Plugin can have it's own controller, model, library, etc.

For more information please visit our wiki <http://github.com/back2arie/Kalkun/wiki>


Official Plugin:
=================
Blacklist Number
External Script
Server Alert
Simple Autoreply
SMS Member
SMS To Email